{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I always said, that's my gangster car, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so then I said, I have been enough of a busboy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, I'm going to become a waiter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went around to the different hotels and I went to a place called the Robert Richter Hotel, which was at that time a restricted hotel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what restricted means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was strictly like the advertising said, churches nearby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, that meant Jews were not allowed in that hotel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I went to see the head, but it turned out to be a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we started talking Germans and Dutch, I knew a little Dutch, too, because I learned it from some-- some of the Dutch Jews in camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he liked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He says, you know cocktails?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, of course I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't have idea what a cocktail was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] He says, we're going to put you in there in the bar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You go-- I had the easiest job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At night, during dinner hour, I went upstairs to the dining room-- can I take your drink order, Martini, whatever it was?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Went down the bar, picked it up, and got tipped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I Made a lot of money compared to all the waiters had-- had to wait to give them a full course meal before they got a dollar.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- so I-- and then at night after dinner, I was the only waiter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had-- you're not going to believe-- we had Pupi Campo with his orchestra there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at that time, he just started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then he went over to the Saxony later on, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
